Collections About Politics and Government

These collections house textual material regarding the lives, research, and events of prominent political figures, including those of Burton K. Wheeler, Wesley A. De’Ewart, William T. Cowan, Harriett Hayne, James Francis O’Connor, Roland R. Renne, Ron Marlenee, and Zales N. Ecton.
